            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>科沃(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:QRVO:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/QRVO\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">QRVO-US</a>)截至台北時間09日02:13股價下跌2.87美元，報53.52美元，跌幅5.09%，成交量2,231,151（股），盤中最高價58.73美元、最低價53.52美元。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.55%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.2%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-0.37%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：-0.32%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>科沃(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:QRVO:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/QRVO\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">QRVO-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-21.13%</li> <li>近 1 月：-26.58%</li> <li>近 3 月：-23.41%</li> <li>近 6 月：-43.81%</li> <li>今年以來：-19.36%</li></ul></section></main>",
